title: Hour 2 - Deshaun Watson Update, Anthony Munoz

description:
Dan updates us on the appeal of Cleveland Browns QB Deshaun Watson's suspension appeal by the NFL. And NFL Hall of Fame OL, Anthony Munoz drops by to talk about life in the trenches.
